## Dual Control Approval Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as Human User
    participant V as VIVIM Vault
    participant C as Company (Rights Node)
    participant M as Marketplace/Export

    U->>V: Request export of Tier 3 content
    V->>V: Check ownership tensor
    V->>C: Send approval request (minimal disclosure)
    
    Note over C: Review packet shows<br/>- Content descriptor<br/>- Provenance<br/>- Classification
    
    C->>V: Approve OR Deny
    
    alt Approved
        V->>M: Execute export (with dual signature)
        M->>U: Export complete
    else Denied
        V->>U: Export denied - company rejected
    end
```

