# Canary System Detail

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> GenerateCanary
    
    state GenerateCanary {
        [*] --> CreatePhrase
        CreatePhrase --> EncodeDID
        EncodeDID --> EmbedInContent
        EmbedInContent --> PlantInVault
    }
    
    PlantInVault --> WaitForModel
    
    state WaitForModel {
        [*] --> Superposition
        Superposition: |canary⟩ = α|undetected⟩ + β|detected⟩
    }
    
    WaitForModel --> ProbeModel: Query model with canary
    ProbeModel --> Detect: Model shows knowledge
    
    state Detect {
        [*] --> Collapse
        Collapse: Wave function collapses
        Collapse --> Record: Record detection event
    }
    
    Detect --> Evidence: Generate proof
    Evidence --> [*]
    
    note right of Superposition: Quantum analogy -<br/>canary exists in<br/>superposition until measured